Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me what you're plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:05.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:06.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:07.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Agency" has nothing to do with this affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I filed a report to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about an overnight trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm concerned about is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...this trip you planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that Suzumiya-san was interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact that it's a privately owned deserted island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said something about a closed circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a closed circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:28.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A mystery term.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It refers to a situation where contact with the outside world has been severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:32.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like being stuck in a mountain villa during a blizzard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:37.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...or finding ourselves in an isolated hostel right when a typhoon drops?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:39.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The concerned parties...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:41.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...find themselves trapped by surrounding circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, closed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:46.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with this trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deserted island remote from civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm were to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would be a closed circle setting...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:55.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...on par with being trapped in a mountain villa during a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:01:00.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're wondering why I'm talking with Koizumi in the middle of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:06.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it would be because I had no way to undo the meeting on that day I had finally recovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...from the Black Monday we got our term exams back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an important meeting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:46.67,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,490)\fs24\pos(340,397)}Remote Island Syndrome (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone had showed up after I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:49.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was planning on the punishment of eternally being It in a game of kick the can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure I don't need to tell you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I hadn't heard a thing about a meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:58.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first SOS Brigade overnight trip of summer vacation has been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:02:59.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Overnight trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Overnight trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are we doing this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The location has already been decided, right... Koizumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:10.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my distant relatives happens to be quite wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:15.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He has enough money to buy a deserted island and build a villa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:18.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That manor was completed just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Be glad, Koizumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For your achievements...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm specially promoting you two ranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and naming you the SOS Brigade Deputy Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:30.53,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0.2\be1\shad0\1c&H000073&\b1\frx20\fry-15\frz15\3c&H000073&\pos(285,297)}DEPUTY CHIEF
