Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:38.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody's jealous of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A four-day, three-night extravagant tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we come, remote island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something fun has to be awaiting us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My role has already been decided, okay?
