Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us consider detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The detectives found in literary work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:01.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...find themselves involved in baffling cases one after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:06.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There wouldn't be a story otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Such incidents are fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They only exist in the unrealistic world of storytelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:13.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...saying such metafictional things...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be a bit too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:22.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Suzumiya-san actually intends to cast herself into such a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she made the SOS Brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...for that purpose, didn't she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to encounter such unrealistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and mysterious incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...one must head to appropriate locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:36.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the detectives of literature...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...get involved in cases in such a fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way something is just going to happen so conveniently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:42.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality is unlike the world of fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:48.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the remote island we are headed towards now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:52.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is most suitable as a location for a murder in the view of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What world do you live in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's gotta be one small world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting it another way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange happenings occur...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...wherever a detective goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans labeled as great detectives...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...possess the supernatural ability to attract trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe myself to be always acting within reasonable boundaries of sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Detectives and closed circles and such matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...are not a result of my own deliberation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was merely tracing Suzumiya-san's thought pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:24.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she wants to become...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:25.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...an ultra detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can you be close in Old Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Next person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun tried to leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:43.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I wasn't planning on bringing you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone was happy to have you along, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:08.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:11.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose that for Asahina's smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:12.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I can let this slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:15.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer till we're there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The trip by ferry takes approximately six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:22.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have arranged for an acquaintance to be waiting at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From there, it will be an hour long voyage by private cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:30.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The remote island and the manor atop it await us at the voyage's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:34.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been there before, so I don't really know what the building looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a strange-looking building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:40.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the name of the person who designed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:40.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do you want to know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't inquire about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he commissioned a somewhat famous architect for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least I remember hearing something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somewhat is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides, a manor that would satisfy Haruhi's expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:57.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would probably look like some gaudy building designed after...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:55.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Second out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:56.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...three straight all-nighters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and during an alcohol-induced stupor while periodically dozing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Island! Manor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything more fitting for the SOS Brigade's summer trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Done! Third out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:12.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The loser has to buy everyone drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want 100% fruit juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have royal milk tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get to order until you're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Remote islands are all about strange incidents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't let anything happen. Please don't let anything happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:31.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The exact characteristics which constitute an incident remain undefined...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I hope that this journey is a pleasant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Sis! Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head up to the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a monster squid will show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Squid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If one shows up, Nagato will have to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sleeping for, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even intend to be serious about this trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a picture of you waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I took a picture of your sleeping face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sleeping face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would Asahina-san secretly take pictures of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:27.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe she's going to put my picture in a cute-looking frame and place it by her bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be really deep in dreamland...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you grinning about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you look like an idiot so you'd best stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:36.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I made Mikuru-chan the temporary SOS Brigade photographer for this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:41.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are important materials needed to leave a record of our club activities for posterity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who decides what to take a picture of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:44.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:48.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How are pictures of me sleeping and waking up worthwhile material?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:52.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture of you sleeping with a stupid look on your face totally oblivious to the dangers of this trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...serves as a warning to future generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An underling snoring away when the chief is awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...goes against morals and natural order and brigade code!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious island awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious island, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not like Panorama Island or Infant Island, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:16.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be fine as long as it doesn't suddenly rise out of the water or start moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:18.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}This is my first time to a mysterious island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing unusual about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a small, lone island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find any monsters or crazy scientists there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}What about Mikuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Have you ever been to one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:27.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}I haven't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your word is the one I trust the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:29.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.38,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\frx18\fry-30\frz15\be1\bord0\shad0.5\4a&H66&\1c&HDBB884&\pos(121,125)}Ferry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.38,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\frx18\fry-30\frz14\be1\bord0\shad0.5\4a&H66&\1c&HDBB884&\pos(451,38)}Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:33.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.72,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H33&\bord2\shad0\fad(0,200)\fs21\be1\pos(352,343)}Mr. Arakawa / Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Mori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.76,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H33&\bord2\shad0\fad(300,0)\fs21\be1\pos(352,342)}Sonou Mori / Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to meet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:45.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my irreplaceable friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have prepared a boat over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:53.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a half hour voyage by boat to reach my master's island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:56.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I must apologize for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes it a remote island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget half an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take as many hours as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a remote island out in the deep seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon. Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You should look happier about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A manor on a remote island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And even a suspicious-looking butler and maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You could search all of Japan and only find two other islands like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You couldn't even find two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:32.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she trying to pick up on maid mannerisms from Mori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She sure gets serious about weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the House of Black Death or Lilas Manor or Koketsu Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a name along those lines, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a bunch of hidden mechanisms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the architect died of unnatural causes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or there's a room where any occupant ends up dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You could hear a pin drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the master of the manor wear a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe three gentle sisters exist inside his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then everyone disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:06.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There has been nothing as of this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:09.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's a pretty high chance something will happen in the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:10.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the manor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks kind of normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the master of the manor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks rather young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also an invited guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:35.36,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H33&\bord2\shad0\fad(0,300)\fs21\be1\pos(352,342)}Yutaka Tamaru / Master's Younger Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The master's younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka Tamaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've met him once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us these things earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first I've heard about any other guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:11.26,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H33&\bord2\shad0\fs21\be1\pos(352,342)}Keiichi Tamaru / Master of Manor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:09.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to express my sincere gratitude for your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:20.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly appreciate the opportunity to stay in such a wonderful manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,On behalf of everyone here, I offer our thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:28.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are different from what I heard from Itsuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I got the impression you were more of a frank girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:32.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, big guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:38.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving right along, have any strange incidents happened in this manor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:43.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And does this island have any ominous nicknames or terrifying legends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in that kind of stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:51.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,While unfortunate for your interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...no incidents have occurred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The building was only completed a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:01.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I haven't heard anything particularly sinister about this island's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a deserted island, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not stand here and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Western-style house so feel free to leave your shoes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more ordinary than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go with one person per room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the doors can be locked, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't automatic so you can't lock yourself out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'd appreciate it if you didn't lose the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Sister can stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The absence of anything suspicious is what makes this suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what if there was something that looked suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:38.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, as far as she's concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...nothing can be considered free from suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:47.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured out what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:48.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's happened yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My gut tells me that the culprit is the master of the manor, Keiichi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His first victim will be Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're guests here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop thinking about that dangerous stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Act more like a high schooler, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have a swim first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:15.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that people go to the beach for the sole purpose of swimming is no exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:16.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, even Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:21.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...can't be truly wishing for someone to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:31.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This moment would be the highlight of this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is what you call a trip to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Each person has his or her own way of having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,People should spend their leisure time doing activities they enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We must be sure to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...provide Suzumiya-san adequate entertainment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...to prevent her from being bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon! Koizumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which one's the beach ball!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}This stuff's yummy, Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The butler, Arakawa, also serves as chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite impressive, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to offer my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Call him over later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Here. This one's good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:39.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a refill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like green peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't eat properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:49.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't grow up to be like Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't get a chance to enjoy such a feast very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:59.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really all free?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If only the school cafeteria was this generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:11.50,HaruhiEDRo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0\fscx100\fscy135\bord1.2\1c&H282F44&\3c&H686B61&\an8\fry30\be1\fs60\frz-90\pos(641,155)}50 Shots
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so we...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...taking full advantage of Mr. Tamaru's hospitality...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...made it through the day without anything unusual happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:25.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:29.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it would have been helpful if things had ended here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Snake! Snaaake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The morning of the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was suddenly storming outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My master is not a morning person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a hard time waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:49.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His absence in the morning is discourteous...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I hope you can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotten luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A typhoon just had to show up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be a fast-moving one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll pass in a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:02.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Storms both come and go without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:06.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there wasn't anything about a typhoon in the forecast yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just whose head did this storm pop out of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're really stranded on a remote island in the middle of a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a once-in-a-lifetime situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange incident just may happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The waves appear to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...far stronger than acceptable conditions for taking the boat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:29.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Through Haruhi's will, we have unwillingly found ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...trapped on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A closed circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:39.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being unable to go outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...we spent the day in the game room in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Ultra Miracle Excellent Trick Serve!
