Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:04.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:05.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably worth ten thousand points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:08.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's thirty-two thousand points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a good thing we aren't playing for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I can join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:18.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is transferring money between banks fraud?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some work to finish up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'll excuse myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Keiichi Tamaru and Yutaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the Arakawa-san-Mori-san combo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:46.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They seem pretty normal for acquaintances of Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We seem to need a few more characters before a strange incident can occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:01.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around then say "I love you" while looking backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's number two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:11.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Put more feeling into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:20.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:22.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:23.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The king is ordering you to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:27.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a capricious king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or wait, isn't Haruhi always like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was expecting to be able to just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:40.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...blissfully breeze through the remainder of this chapter of adolescence...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but as they say, it ain't over till the fat lady sings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know exactly which fat lady is doing the singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:46.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or where she's planning on doing her singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I find out where she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:51.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'd like to put her out of commission for a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:00.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Overnight trips are all about pillow fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:04.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can you possibly have so much energy after staying up most of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A pillow fight, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would explain why after breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Suzumiya-san went around all the rooms on the second floor and gathered up the pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All you can throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:15.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she confiscates our weapons before it even starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Arakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:27.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Mori went to Yutaka-sama's room just now, but he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-san wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no signs that the bed had been slept in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Searching his usual spots yielded nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about asking Keiichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:38.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried contacting the master's room through the intercom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but there was no reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-san is missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Keiichi-san isn't responding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:51.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it directly, that would be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about checking inside Keiichi-san's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have an extra key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The master's room is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:01.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The master holds the only spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:05.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are documents concerning his work inside so it's a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We should go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Yuki and Mikuru-chan, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:14.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Sis stays here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san? Keiichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Respond if you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:36.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our last option.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We must break the door down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot afford to lose any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it only possible to break down doors in TV dramas?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:17.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:19.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've gotta be kidding...?
